00:29:31.359 --> 00:29:33.400
And so going to Microsoft,

00:29:33.400 --> 00:29:36.239
which is such a large organization,

00:29:36.239 --> 00:29:40.079
that there are almost inevitably five different departments

00:29:40.079 --> 00:29:42.239
