00:51:16.679 --> 00:51:20.520
That's actually one of the ways I like started using

00:51:20.520 --> 00:51:22.719
chat to BT was just saying like,

00:51:22.719 --> 00:51:26.800
how should I change this to adjust the tone

00:51:26.800 --> 00:51:28.399
the way I'm presenting it?

